text: Novaya Otrada () is a rural locality (a village) in Otradinsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 129 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 8 km from Yermolayevo, 7 km from Staraya Otrada. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Novaya Otrada
